Chicago: Mapping Enterprise Zones and CTA L stops

Emma Bonanno

9/4/2021

Loading Packages

library(sf)
library(tidyverse)
library(ggthemes)
library(ggspatial)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)

Downloading and Naming Data

Ezones <- st_read("https://data.cityofchicago.org/api/geospatial/64xf-pyvh?method=export&format=KML") 
## Reading layer `Layer #0' from data source 
##   `https://data.cityofchicago.org/api/geospatial/64xf-pyvh?method=export&format=KML' 
##   using driver `KML'
## Simple feature collection with 6 features and 2 fields
## Geometry type: MULTIPOLYGON
## Dimension:     XY
## Bounding box:  xmin: -87.79058 ymin: 41.64456 xmax: -87.52446 ymax: 42.00532
## Geodetic CRS:  WGS 84
Lstops <- st_read("https://data.cityofchicago.org/download/4qtv-9w43/application%2Fxml")
## Reading layer `CTA_RailStations' from data source 
##   `https://data.cityofchicago.org/download/4qtv-9w43/application%2Fxml' 
##   using driver `KML'
## Simple feature collection with 144 features and 2 fields
## Geometry type: POINT
## Dimension:     XYZ
## Bounding box:  xmin: -87.90185 ymin: 41.72238 xmax: -87.60586 ymax: 42.07315
## z_range:       zmin: 0 zmax: 0
## Geodetic CRS:  WGS 84

Practicing with Plots

Lstops_plot <- ggplot(Lstops) +
  geom_sf() 
Lstops_plot

ggplot(Lstops) +
  geom_sf(shape = 17, color = "blue") 

ggplot(Lstops) +
  geom_sf(shape = 18, color = "red", size = 0.5) 

ggplot(Lstops) +
  geom_sf(shape = 18, color = "red", alpha = 0.1) 

ggplot(Lstops) +
  geom_sf() +
  geom_sf(data = Ezones) 

ggplot() +
  geom_sf(data = Ezones) +
  geom_sf(data = Lstops, color = "red") 

ggplot() +
  geom_sf(data = Ezones, color = "red",
                        fill = "red",
                        alpha = 0.5) +
  geom_sf(data = Lstops, color = "blue", size = 0.5)

ggplot() +
  geom_sf(data = Ezones, color = NA,alpha = 0.5,
                        aes(fill = "Enterprise Zones")) +
  geom_sf(data = Lstops, color = "blue") +
  scale_fill_manual(values = "red", name = "")

ggplot() +
  geom_sf(data = Ezones, color = NA,alpha = 0.5,
                        aes(fill = "Enterprise Zones")) +
  geom_sf(data = Lstops,
          size = 0.5,
          aes(color = "CTA - L stops")) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = "red", name = "") +
  scale_color_manual(values = "blue", name = "")

ggplot() +
  geom_sf(data = Ezones, color = NA,alpha = 0.5,
                        aes(fill = "Enterprise Zones")) +
  geom_sf(data = Lstops,
          size = 0.5,
          aes(color = "CTA - L stops")) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = "red", name = "") +
  scale_color_manual(values = "blue", name = "") +
  theme(panel.background = element_rect(fill = "white"),
        legend.key = element_rect(fill = "white"))

ggplot() +
  geom_sf(data = Ezones, color = NA,alpha = 0.5,
                        aes(fill = "Enterprise Zones")) +
  geom_sf(data = Lstops,
          size = 0.5,
          aes(color = "CTA - L stops")) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = "red", name = "") +
  scale_color_manual(values = "blue", name = "") +
  theme_void()

ggplot() +
  geom_sf(data = Ezones, color = NA,alpha = 0.5,
                        aes(fill = "Enterprise Zones")) +
  geom_sf(data = Lstops,
          size = 0.5,
          aes(color = "CTA - L stops")) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = "red", name = "") +
  scale_color_manual(values = "blue", name = "") +
  theme_map()

ggplot(Lstops) + 
  annotation_map_tile(zoomin = 0, progress = "none") +
  geom_sf()+
  labs(caption = "Map tiles and data by OpenStreetMap")
## Loading required namespace: raster

ggplot(Lstops) + 
  geom_sf() +
  geom_sf(data = Ezones) +
  annotation_map_tile(zoomin = 0, progress = "none", type = "stamenbw") +
  geom_sf()+
  labs(caption = "Map tiles and data by OpenStreetMap")

ggplot() +
  annotation_map_tile(zoomin = 0, progress = "none", type = "cartolight")  +
  geom_sf() +
  labs(caption = "Map tiles and data by OpenStreetMap")+
  geom_sf(data = Ezones, color = "red",
                        fill = "red",
                        alpha = 0.5) +
  geom_sf(data = Lstops, color = "blue", size = 0.5) 

ggplot() +
  annotation_map_tile(zoomin = 0, progress = "none", type = "cartolight")  +
  geom_sf() +
  labs(caption = "Map tiles and data by OpenStreetMap")+
  geom_sf(data = Ezones, color = NA,alpha = 0.5,
                        aes(fill = "Enterprise Zones")) +
  geom_sf(data = Lstops,
          size = 0.5,
          aes(color = "CTA - L stops")) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = "red", name = "") +
  scale_color_manual(values = "blue", name = "") +
  theme_void()

ggplot() +
  annotation_map_tile(zoomin = 0, progress = "none", type = "cartolight")  +
  geom_sf() +
  labs(caption = "Map tiles and data by OpenStreetMap")+
  geom_sf(data = Ezones, color = "red",alpha = 0.2,
                        aes(fill = "Enterprise Zones")) +
  geom_sf(data = Lstops,
          size = 0.5,
          aes(color = "CTA - L stops")) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = "red", name = "") +
  scale_color_manual(values = "blue", name = "") +
  theme_void()
